data.name: grdChiryoGubun.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT A.CODE , A.CODE_NAME FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT A.CODE CODE ,A.CODE_NAME CODE_NAME FROM DRG0120 B ,INV0102 A WHERE A.CODE_TYPE = '34' AND A.CODE2 = 'A' AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.CHIRYO_GUBUN = A.CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND NVL(B.BOGYONG_GUBUN,'%') LIKE :f_bogyong_gubun AND (( NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM DRG0120 Z , DRG0123 Y , OCS0103 X WHERE X.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_jaeryo_code AND X.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND X.JAERYO_CODE = Y.JAERYO_CODE AND X.HOSP_CODE = Y.HOSP_CODE AND Y.CODE_TYPE = '34' AND Y.CODE = Z.CHIRYO_GUBUN AND Y.HOSP_CODE = Z.HOSP_CODE ) )OR :f_use_yn = 'N' ) ) A UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT C.CODE CODE ,C.CODE_NAME CODE_NAME FROM DRG0120 D ,INV0102 C ,DRG0123 B ,OCS0103 A WHERE A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_jaeryo_code AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.JAERYO_CODE = B.JAERYO_CODE AND A.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE = '34' AND B.CODE_TYPE = C.CODE_TYPE AND B.CODE = C.CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE = C.HOSP_CODE AND D.CHIRYO_GUBUN = B.CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND NVL(D.BOGYONG_GUBUN,'%') LIKE :f_bogyong_gubun AND :f_use_yn = 'Y' ORDER BY 1

data.name: grdDrg0120.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT Y.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE , Y.BOGYONG_NAME BOGYONG_NAME , DECODE(Z.CODE, '10', Y.BOGYONG_NAME, Z.CODE_NAME) BLOCK_GUBUN , FN_DRG_LOAD_DRG0102(Y.BOGYONG_GUBUN, '31') BOGYONG_GUBUN FROM INV0102 Z , DRG0120 Y WHERE Y.CHIRYO_GUBUN = :f_chiryo_gubun AND NVL(Y.BANGHYANG,'4') = NVL(:f_banghyang,'4') AND Y.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND Z.CODE_TYPE = '32' AND Z.CODE = Y.BLOCK_GUBUN AND Z.HOSP_CODE = Y.HOSP_CODE AND Z.CODE2 = 'A' AND ( NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM DRG0120 ZZ , DRG0123 YY , OCS0103 XX WHERE XX.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_jaeryo_code AND XX.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND XX.JAERYO_CODE = YY.JAERYO_CODE AND XX.HOSP_CODE = YY.HOSP_CODE AND YY.CODE_TYPE = '32' AND YY.CODE = ZZ.BLOCK_GUBUN AND YY.HOSP_CODE = ZZ.HOSP_CODE AND ZZ.CHIRYO_GUBUN = :f_chiryo_gubun ) OR :f_use_yn = 'N' ) UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT C.BOGYONG_CODE ,C.BOGYONG_NAME ,DECODE(B.CODE,'10',C.BOGYONG_NAME, B.CODE_NAME) BLOCK_GUBUN ,FN_DRG_LOAD_DRG0102(C.BOGYONG_GUBUN, '31') FROM DRG0120 C ,INV0102 B ,DRG0123 A WHERE A.JAERYO_CODE = :o_jaeryo_code AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.CODE_TYPE = '32' AND B.CODE_TYPE = A.CODE_TYPE AND B.CODE = A.CODE AND B.CODE2 = 'A' AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.CHIRYO_GUBUN = :f_chiryo_gubun AND NVL(C.BANGHYANG, '4') = NVL(:f_banghyang,'4') AND C.BLOCK_GUBUN = A.CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND NVL(C.BOGYONG_GUBUN,'%') LIKE :f_bogyong_gubun AND :f_use_yn = 'Y' AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM DRG0122 Z WHERE Z.JAERYO_CODE = A.JAERYO_CODE AND Z.BOGYONG_CODE = C.BOGYONG_CODE AND Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE ) ORDER BY 1

data.name: grdBaseBogyongCode.QuerySQL
data.value:
SELECT '0' GUBUN , B.BOGYONG_CODE , FN_OCS_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(B.BOGYONG_CODE) BOGYONG_NAME, NVL(C.BOGYONG_CODE, 'N') USER_YN, B.BOGYONG_GUBUN
FROM DRG0120 B ,OCS0208 C WHERE B.BUNRYU1 = '6' AND B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.HOSP_CODE(+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE(+) = B.BOGYONG_CODE ORDER BY 2, B.SORY_KEY

data.name: grdOCS0208.QuerySQL
data.value:
SELECT '0' GUBUN , A.BOGYONG_CODE , FN_OCS_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(A.BOGYONG_CODE) BOGYONG_NAME, 'Y', B.BOGYONG_GUBUN, A.SEQ
FROM OCS0208 A, DRG0120 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.DOCTOR = :f_doctor AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.BOGYONG_CODE = A.BOGYONG_CODE AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNRYU1 = '6'
UNION
SELECT '1' GUBUN , B.BOGYONG_CODE , FN_OCS_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(B.BOGYONG_CODE) BOGYONG_NAME, NVL(C.BOGYONG_CODE, 'N') USER_YN, B.BOGYONG_GUBUN, B.SORY_KEY
FROM DRG0120 B ,OCS0208 C WHERE B.BUNRYU1 = '6' AND B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.HOSP_CODE (+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.BOGYONG_CODE(+) = B.BOGYONG_CODE AND C.DOCTOR (+) = :f_doctor
ORDER BY 1, 6, 2 --, B.SORY_KEY --ORDER BY A.SEQ
